snippet.title: Gex Jr. Demo for PSX
snippet.description:
A short demo of the unreleased and unannounced game Gex Jr. for the PlayStation.

This demo was made by ImageBuilder and is dated January 25, 2001.

The release of this demo has prompted several online publications reporting to falsely claim this to be a "leak".. The source material containing this build has been legally obtained and has not been subject to a breach of any contractual obligation or hacking or stealing in any form. Furthermore, this build is provided below for the means of historical preservation purposes only.

https://archive.org/details/gex-jr.-january-25-2001-prototype
